---
import BaseLayout from "@components/base/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title={"Features"} description={"This is the features page."}>
  <div class="w-full p-4">
    <div class="mb-14 mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="glass rounded-lg p-8 intersect:animate-fadeUp opacity-0">
        <article class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          <h1>Features</h1>
          <h2>Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            Astrogon is an AI powered student management system designed to
            streamline the educational experience. It is tailored to meet the
            needs of both students and educators of FAST NUCES. It comprises of
            some of the most relevant features that enhance the learning
            process.
          </p>
          <h2>Psychological Insights</h2>
          <p>
            Astrogon applies cognitive and motivational psychology to
            personalize learning. Adaptive quizzes are designed around
            Vygotsky’s Zone of Proximal Development, keeping tasks challenging
            yet achievable to sustain engagement and flow. The profile analyzer
            aligns learning paths with individual goals, supporting
            self-determination and self-awareness. Together, these features
            nurture confidence, motivation, and continuous growth.
          </p>
          <h2>Main Features</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <h3>Quizzes with adaptive difficulty</h3>
            </li>
            <p>
              Our AI-driven quiz system intelligently adjusts question
              difficulty in real time based on each student’s performance,
              keeping challenges within their optimal learning zone. It can
              generate quizzes for any course or topic, creating fresh, unique
              MCQs every time—ensuring no two quizzes are ever the same. This
              promotes engagement, mastery, and truly personalized assessment
              experiences.
            </p>
            <li>
              <h3>Student Profile Analyzer</h3>
            </li>
            <p>
              Our Student Profile Analyzer uses AI to create a personalized
              academic and career roadmap. By evaluating a student’s CGPA,
              major, quiz performance, and stated goals—along with preferred
              industries and target roles—it generates a detailed report with
              actionable insights. The system identifies academic strengths,
              skill gaps, and growth areas, offering tailored advice for
              improving performance and aligning studies with long-term career
              ambitions.
            </p>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
